{"tid":411153,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李 亞 男 擇 偶 著 重 身 高 ： 一 定 要 高 過 我","createTime":"2017-09-23T14:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T22:02:31.000Z","uid":36253,"like":560,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4c41d2d385439162c94c8be14fad323073ab4dab","tid":411153,"uid":36253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:29:15.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】李亞男與楊秀惠昨日介紹無綫明珠台新節目，李亞男一時貪玩，將手銬鎖起來，幾經辛苦才解開。李亞男長得高大，拍劇時難找男拍檔配合，那麼選男友是否也很難？她說：「一定要高過我，黃長興也不合格；不過，我現時專心工作，也不想找男友。」她稍後會到湖南擔任《舞動奇跡》司儀，「希望明年可以參賽」。 <br />\n<br />\n楊秀惠緋聞男友孫耀威撞車傷及鼻子，她說：「我有致電問候，但助手接聽，若他在美容方面需要幫手，我一定會幫。」身為女友的她不嬲孫耀威只由助手接電話？她說：「我只是女性朋友，不是女友，只要他沒事，我便放心。」 <br />\n<br />\n記者：楊敏麗"},{"pid":"f9fded0a50579d62bafff0ff27c1e890937b3d66","tid":411153,"uid":10296,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:39:52.000Z","msg":"笑撚左"},{"pid":"b99fdf5a859bd4c039ac68acfb2d0cebe26e26b1","tid":411153,"uid":23451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416131db8c1fc118f8cdf1f6c813a307e2743ffc","tid":411153,"uid":75694,"like":351,"dislike":2,"score":349,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:41:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終極bin c"},{"pid":"6775412dfe642af463b7dd3781e428e50e9d25c5","tid":411153,"uid":1139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:41:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27649d8a77e4e0984e0b613d03900287af9bc3eb","tid":411153,"uid":34098,"like":511,"dislike":2,"score":509,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"500萬港幣可以當1cm。你有無"},{"pid":"d1d476f937e0f32e41ef4b95a74f68a9cf61c2f9","tid":411153,"uid":96146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:42:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終極bin c</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj